title: The Love Scene in Top Gun: Maverick
itunes:title: The Love Scene in Top Gun: Maverick
description: A Pennsylvania man who sought treatment for jaw pain murders his chiropractor. The author of "how to murder your husband" blog was convicted of murdering her husband and a movie theatre chain accidentally showed porn to sold out auditoriums across the country instead of pay per view WWE wrestling.
